        "description": "Demon GazeBuffArlott possesses a demonic eye that will Mark enemy units near Arlott that become affected by control effects for 7s.The eye will also automatically Mark a nearby enemy hero every 7s. Notes Demon Gaze is applied to enemies within 5.5 unit, even if  Arlott is unsighted to them. Demon Gaze will only auto apply to, and in the following priority: Enemies without Mark. Targetable enemies. Visible enemies. Nearest enemies. Become CC immune does not remove Mark disappears when the unit dies. Demon Gaze is independent from  Arlott. The ability keeps its cooldown when he dies. Reapplying Mark through control effects refreshes the duration.",
